{"id":465031,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":4,"day":4}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"200","ytitle":"","mtitle":"出路只有一条","ftitle":"","authors":["王森"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明在越南扩大战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却满嘴扯谈‘和平’；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收起你那虚伪的一套吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊，你这天下第一名骗子!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你犯下的罪行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一件都骇人听闻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你欠下的血债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一笔都必须还清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在农村，在城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是复仇的人民；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前线，在后方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处有解放的炮声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要炸毁所有的飞机场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要捣烂所有的‘战略村’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神圣的南越土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊，岂容你安身!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“特种战争”早破产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒气更救不了命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出路吗?只有一条——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊，卷起铺盖滚!"}]}